title: Player Attack S03E16 720p HDTV h264-Berg
description:
This week, Jonny Robot has emerged from the world of The Witcher 3, bleary eyed and a little dazed, and we convinced him to tell us all about his adventures before he disappeared again.

Jessica proves that she probably should never operate heavy machinery, with a look at sequel/reboot/90s throwback Carmageddon: Reincarnation.

...and we head to Oz Comic-Con in search of cosplayers. With both Eve Beauregard and Keith Zen in the same place, who knows what else we might find!

Plus, of course, we have all the latest gaming news - this is Player Attack!
